      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical R2023.1, FDA in-house FEA code v4.2, and DePuy Synthes proprietary solver each have documented installation qualification reports and regression test suites. Version control records confirm no mid-study code changes. SQA level assessed as Gradation 2, meeting the required level."
