      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems with known analytical solutions must be used to verify correct implementation of element formulations and contact algorithms relevant to the pedicle screw construct model.",
      "rationale": "All three codes verified against NAFEMS benchmark LE1 (linear elasticity) and a Hertzian contact patch test. Results agree with analytical solutions within 1% for stress and 0.5% for displacement. Code verification documented in supplementary verification report V-2024-01."
