      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation performed on three mesh densities (coarse ~85k, medium ~210k, fine ~520k elements). GCI for stiffness QoI = 0.8%, yield force = 1.1%, force at 40 mm = 0.7%. Production mesh (medium) selected; all GCI values below 2% threshold."
