      "acceptanceCriteria": "N≥10 experimental constructs from production lots with documented traceability; sample dimensions verified by CMM prior to testing.",
      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested, drawn from two production lots with full traceability to material certificates. All construct dimensions verified by CMM; mean outer diameter 7.48 mm (±0.02 mm), consistent with nominal. Samples distributed across two independent laboratories to assess inter-laboratory variability. Test samples factor assessed at Gradation 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
