      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Testing must replicate at least two clinically relevant loading magnitudes or configurations; environmental conditions (temperature, humidity) must be controlled and documented.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single loading rate (5 mm/min) and single construct configuration per ASTM F1717. Only one test condition explored; multi-rate or multi-configuration testing not conducted. Environmental conditions (23°C ± 2°C, ambient humidity) documented at both laboratories. Achieved level Gradation 2 due to single test condition; this factor is below the required Gradation 3 and represents a known gap in the validation evidence."
    },
