      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Computational model boundary conditions and material inputs must demonstrably correspond to the experimental setup; any differences must be quantified and shown to have negligible effect on QoIs.",
      "rationale": "Experimental boundary conditions (pin-in-slot fixture geometry, crosshead displacement control, construct span) replicated in FEA to within CMM measurement uncertainty. Friction coefficient in model (μ=0.3) consistent with measured values from fixture qualification tests. Differences between nominal FEA inputs and measured experimental parameters quantified; maximum QoI sensitivity to these differences <1.8%. Equivalency assessed at Gradation 3."
    },
