      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (percentage difference and E/uval) computed for all three QoIs; all metrics must satisfy pre-established acceptance bounds.",
      "rationale": "Percentage differences: stiffness 2.9%, yield force 3.8%, force at 40 mm 2.2% — all within the <10% bound. E/uval values: 0.61, 0.84, 0.49 — all below 1.96. Bounds established a priori in the validation plan (VP-2023-07) before experimental data were unblinded. Output comparison factor assessed at Gradation 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
